Interface VirtualMachine.UpdateStages.WithUnmanagedDataDisk

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    VirtualMachine.Update, VirtualMachine.UpdateStages.WithSystemAssignedIdentityBasedAccessOrUpdate
    Enclosing interface:
    VirtualMachine.UpdateStages

    public static interface VirtualMachine.UpdateStages.WithUnmanagedDataDisk
    The stage of a virtual machine definition allowing to specify unmanaged data disk configuration.
